These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia
City: hannover, marseilles
There are 2 different nationalities: american, japanese
House: victorian, futuristic
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
2. the american is on the right of the futuristic house##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Flower       | zinnia       | bellflower |
| City         | marseilles | hannover  |
| Nationality       | japanese    | american    |
| House   | futuristic       | victorian      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, march
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, aconite
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Game      | bridge     | mah-jongg |
| Birthday           | january | march      |
| Transport   | roller  | quad-bike      |
| Flower         | daisy | aconite     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, cycling
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, azalea
City: san-francisco, liverpool
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, gardening
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Sport      | golf | cycling  |
| Flower          | daisy    | azalea   |
| City   | liverpool  | san-francisco   |
| Hobby     | gardening     | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, iris
House: wooden, ranch-style
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, mouse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person who growsiris is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Flower      | aconite       | iris |
| House          | ranch-style         | wooden    |
| Pet           | mouse | guinea-pig    |
| Sport   | rugby           | snowboarding   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog
There 2 different types of food: corn, nectarine
House: townhouse, wooden
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Game         | mah-jongg | backgammon   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | hedgehog       |
| Food         | corn   | nectarine |
| House     | wooden    | townhouse     |

