.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-7::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, dancing
There are 2 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, december
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, action
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |
| Hobby          | dancing | collecting  |
| Color   | blood-red   | grey     |
| Birthday         | september  | december |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel       | action    |

