The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, disco
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, handball
City: paris, london
1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |      2       |
| Nationality         | colombian            | egyptian  |
| Music-Genre           | disco | gospel |
| Sport   | biathlon           | handball       |
| City     | paris            | london        |

