.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros
City: edinburgh, rome
2 different games are played: go, bridge
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Cigar   | game         | oliveros    |
| City       | rome     | edinburgh  |
| Game      | go | bridge     |
| Birthday        | november     | december |

