.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, basketball
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, scientific
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, coach
2 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg
1. the coach is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the coach is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Sport          | swimming | basketball |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | scientific      |
| Job   | lawyer | coach    |
| Game           | poker    | mah-jongg    |

