.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: thai, canadian
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, pop
House: craftsman, townhouse
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea
1. the thai is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
2. the thai is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the craftsman house is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | canadian | thai     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | pop |
| House           | craftsman          | townhouse    |
| Beverage     | iced-tea            | cola       |

 